inlineContent.text: A quantity sample contains one or more

objects. Each quantity represents a single piece of data with a single numeric value and the value’s associated units. For example, you can use quantity samples to record the user’s height, the user’s current heart rate, or the number of calories in a hamburger. HealthKit provides a wide range of quantity types, letting you track many different health and fitness features.
